{"tid":2458011,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國爆紅燒酒代言 清純素人堪比國民初戀","createTime":"2021-03-23T06:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T10:49:49.000Z","uid":9573,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"41c0e42b9eebb054b1d7ce485bf4879f99e83559","tid":2458011,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:03:06.000Z","msg":"燒酒地位在韓國可謂重要，所以燒酒品牌一向都會找知名藝人代言，換句話說，能夠勝任燒酒代言人的人，就必對會成為韓國的「大勢」名人。最近燒酒品牌就打破傳統，找來素人做代言，在低光源環境下依然能帶來絕佳的成像表現，竟意外令素人爆紅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BB1eoWzX.img?h=1541&amp;w=1119&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=406&amp;y=470\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBB1eoWzX.img%3Fh%3D1541%26w%3D1119%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D406%26y%3D470&h=4ebc3c05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以往燒酒代言人一角的競爭激烈。往年有國民歌手IU李知恩，國民初戀秀智和人間香奈兒Jennie擔任代言，精準對焦捕捉不想錯過的每一個關鍵時刻。而且海報宣傳一出，就必定掀起媒體和公眾討論，可見地位非同小可。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BB1eoYuG.img?h=1389&amp;w=1119&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=315&amp;y=405\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBB1eoYuG.img%3Fh%3D1389%26w%3D1119%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D315%26y%3D405&h=ee29bda1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年燒酒品牌一反常態，請來素人李書賢（이소현），擔任代言人，但反應竟不比以往遜色。樣貌姣好的李書賢，雖然不比當紅明星有名，但素人親切的臉孔，調校出音樂人期望的理想高音質，搭配立體聲喇叭，為大眾提供新鮮感，瞬間令她爆紅。更有網民指她某些角度與國民初戀秀智相像。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/F8GSkb_Qjtj7mrBy9uXJWC6S_maEkclwdYW4of9cgVHri2fvZTgZxR1Og8px5tOdpwWKl2TeyJZAGuT7SbbbdEOGhqIW-WaiL7I07vs0bLapue8CtJWg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FF8GSkb_Qjtj7mrBy9uXJWC6S_maEkclwdYW4of9cgVHri2fvZTgZxR1Og8px5tOdpwWKl2TeyJZAGuT7SbbbdEOGhqIW-WaiL7I07vs0bLapue8CtJWg&h=168384a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但原來私底下，李書賢也很喜歡在個人Instagram和YouTube頻道上，分享生活點滴和身邊所見所聞。新世代的她，搭載大容量4000mAh電池及無線充電功能，雖然不活躍於傳統娛樂平台上，但在不同社交媒體上就很受歡迎，擁有約8.7萬的追蹤者。"},{"pid":"eafc2205e5a50a912abc189d06c8e04ab19bdd4f","tid":2458011,"uid":13558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:05:43.000Z","msg":"估到有朱千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c299eb0a28231deb9ae8caa3fb19164b285053","tid":2458011,"uid":34999,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:07:14.000Z","msg":"新世代的她，搭載大容量4000mAh電池及無線充電功能<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a99245389e478a4f18a5f4e424c52eb1cfe1c1","tid":2458011,"uid":394010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9c299eb0a28231deb9ae8caa3fb19164b285053","tid":2458011,"uid":34999,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:07:14.000Z","msg":"新世代的她，搭載大容量4000mAh電池及無線充電功能<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:15:41.000Z","msg":"笑到gap gap聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314a96f6b0fd2f2e19ecd1e9d4a464a9ca03a6d9","tid":2458011,"uid":2757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:23:37.000Z","msg":"你食朱千雪 我食長齋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb5fd86399e32d55e8f31a7d8830c253c4f0096","tid":2458011,"uid":148835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:24:21.000Z","msg":"但素人親切的臉孔，調校出音樂人期望的理想高音質，搭配立體聲喇叭，為大眾提供新鮮感<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe247169121d462ce4a50c974dda82675ee6751f","tid":2458011,"uid":2757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"314a96f6b0fd2f2e19ecd1e9d4a464a9ca03a6d9","tid":2458011,"uid":2757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:23:37.000Z","msg":"你食朱千雪 我食長齋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:25:30.000Z","msg":"怕日出一到 科興瓦解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6511372ba857389262f981eb2e49c3e35217ed4a","tid":2458011,"uid":174654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:32:12.000Z","msg":"千雪回來了"},{"pid":"d675455d16bb6b1709f7535a9d3943bab7a664fd","tid":2458011,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:37:49.000Z","msg":"若有巴返黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474a721e9ffbbc70d4f69e0dffbe407aa2743e2e","tid":2458011,"uid":60145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:56:57.000Z","msg":"李娜恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998ee66d79fc89d0e9e70cad274965a49e6aafea","tid":2458011,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:09:50.000Z","msg":"呢排密咗手<i